{"word":"συμβούλομαι","slug":"συμβούλομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συμβούλομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσομαι</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-βεβούλημαι</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to will</i> or <i>to wish with another</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to agree with</i>, <el>τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:—<a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to consent</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}